[domain]
initially soilDry
initially !pumpActive
startPump causes !soilDry if !waterLow
startPump causes pumpActive if !waterLow
checkReservoir causes !waterLow
startPump costs 5
checkReservoir costs 2

[queries]
{soilDry} after startPump, checkReservoir
startPump, checkReservoir executable with cost 4
startPump, checkReservoir executable with exact cost 4